<p><b>Human Rights Council 
Twenty-ninth session 
</b></p>
<p>Agenda item 3 
</p>
<p><b>Promotion and protection of all human rights, civil, 
</b></p>
<p><b>political, economic, social and cultural rights, 
</b></p>
<p><b>including the right to development 
</b></p>
<p><b>  Andorra,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Angola,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Australia,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Austria,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Bolivia (Plurinational State of), Bosnia and 
</b></p>
<p><b>Herzegovina,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Botswana, Brazil, Bulgaria,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Cameroon,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Canada,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Congo, Cyprus,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> 
</b></p>
<p><b>Estonia, Ethiopia, France, Georgia,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Germany, Greece,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Guatemala,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Honduras,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> 
</b></p>
<p><b>Hungary,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Iceland,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Indonesia, Ireland, Israel,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Italy,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Japan, Kenya, Lithuania,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> 
</b></p>
<p><b>Luxembourg,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Madagascar,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Mali,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Mexico, Montenegro, Morocco, Nicaragua,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
