</footnote> Paraguay, Peru,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Poland,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
</footnote> Portugal, Republic of Korea, Romania,<footnote name="*">Non-member State of the Human Rights Council. 
